  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nWhen typing, the mention is not displayed in the input field.\r\nCan be sent but in the input field looks like nothing has been entered.\r\nThe issue is not reproducible at the first attempt, i.e need to re-open the chat view.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nMention is visible in the input field\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/105202897-c0782300-5b42-11eb-98bd-c80e7b35b2cb.mp4\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Join public chat\r\n- Re-open the chat\r\n- Type `@`\r\n- Select some user name from the suggestion list\r\n- Send message\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Nightly 20/01\r\n- Operating System: Android",
